SO yesterday was our four month, making this my LONGEST relationship {not including when i went out with Joel, Dan or Tyler} those three were between 6 months - a year. I dont count elementry. so yes, my longest. crazy times, its gone by fast, doesnt even seem like 4 months has past. MMM taste the goodness
so today was a good day, i went to school for first and second, then i went out for lunch, and skipped third. I did some shopping, and got my eyebrows waxed {haha hows that for your eye brow theory kevin}
I went back to school for fourth and started putting together some of my video, its gunna be stellar. well now im sitting around waiting for B!lly to get home from work so i can call him and we can hang out. I'm talkin to my stevie now about all the things she will do in my video, shes my main man, and shes gunna kill herself in the boiler room with an extention cord, oh man im exctied for this.

Things can be soo freegin weird sometimes, everyhting is ok one minute, things are all messed up the next. pft stupid emotions, they get in the way of everyone and everything 
anyways today i got up early, i recieved a phone call from my sister and Arif {i was super excited and i cant wait to chill with him sometime} dont know how she managed that one . . . 
so after that i went to church with papsie, then after he took me to wendys for lunch. Then i went to see Andy and Nicky, and we played grand theft auto st.andres. {pft i got to pick up hoes on the corner, get some, then kill them with my chainsaw so i could get my money back} im lovin the development of video games today,there so realistic . . . then after i played the guitar for a bit, and went on msn, hung out a little while longer then we headed out. now im here waiting for someone fun to come on line cause seeing as i cant walk i cant do anyhting. i got to talk to nick for a bit tonight, that was stellar, i havent seen him since the summer. { crazy time that was ;) }
